Class CleanLinesFilter

    • pl.sudokusolver.recognizerlib.filters.CleanLinesFilter

    IFilter

    public class CleanLinesFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFilter
    This filter clear lines form given matrix.
    This matrix should be "blurable" - have type compatible with blur filter.
